              "id": "MisplacedNullCheck",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "The null check here is misplaced; if the variable 'userDefined' is null there will be a NullPointerException"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "\nThe null check here is misplaced. If the variable is null a `NullPointerException` will be thrown.\nEither the check is useless (the variable will never be `null`) or it is incorrect.\n        "
